This rib brings a "squad" model of repo development to Keelson as an installable
extension: a roster of named team members you author, each surfaced as a
first-class Keelson chat agent and rendered on the canvas substrate. It imports
no harness internals; it attaches solely through the `Rib` contract from
@keelson/shared. Its structure follows the @keelson/rib-chamber rib's surface +
genesis + canvas-board patterns.
